@@TJvCustomEdit.OnMouseLeave
Summary
  Occurs when the mouse pointer moves off the edit control.
Description
  \Write an OnMouseLeave event handler to take specific action when the user moves the mouse off the
  edit control. For example, you can use this event to undo changes that were made in an OnMouseEnter
  event handler.
See Also
  HotTrack, OnMouseEnter
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomEdit.OnParentColorChange
Summary
  Occurs when the color property for the parent of the edit control changes.
Description
  \Write an OnParentColorChange event to take specific action when the ParentColor property changes.
